data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath colonial home in Lakewood, Ohio is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled in a vibrant neighborhood, it offers easy access to a variety of restaurants and the scenic Metroparks. The property features plenty of character and charm. With its desirable location and inviting layout, this home presents a wonderful opportunity for those seeking a cozy and well-connected living space in Lakewood.
